{
  "$schema": "https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/userguide/bucket-policies.html",
  "_comment": [
    "Cloudflare R2 bucket policy for roost (project distribution v2).",
    "R2 uses S3-compatible IAM policy syntax — this file is the source of",
    "truth, applied via `wrangler r2 bucket cors` or via R2 dashboard.",
    "",
    "Per-tenant chunk paths: project-content/{siteId}/{hash[0:2]}/{hash}",
    "Per-tenant manifest paths: project-manifests/{siteId}/{folderId}/{manifestId}.json",
    "",
    "Default-deny posture: anonymous reads return 403, listed buckets are",
    "not enumerable. All access goes through signed URLs issued by the API",
    "(/api/chunks/upload-urls, /api/chunks/download-urls). The signed URL",
    "issuer enforces per-tenant scope based on caller's siteId claim.",
    "",
    "Buckets:",
    "  owlette-prod-content    — production chunks (R2 EU jurisdiction TBD)",
    "  owlette-prod-manifests  — production manifests",
    "  owlette-dev-content     — development chunks",
    "  owlette-dev-manifests   — development manifests",
    "",
    "Server-side chunk verification (Cloud Function with FILE_ATTRIBUTE_REPARSE_POINT",
    "trigger) re-streams uploaded objects, computes SHA-256, and deletes if",
    "the filename does not match the content hash. See functions/src/chunkVerify.ts."
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "DenyAnonymousAccess",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-content",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-content/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-manifests",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-manifests/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-content",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-content/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-manifests",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-manifests/*"
      ],
      "Condition": {
        "StringNotEquals": {
          "aws:PrincipalType": "Service"
        },
        "Null": {
          "aws:SignedRequest": "true"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowSignedUrlReadsAndWrites",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:HeadObject"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-content/project-content/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-manifests/project-manifests/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-content/project-content/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-manifests/project-manifests/*"
      ],
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "aws:SignedRequest": "true"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyBucketEnumeration",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListAllMyBuckets",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-content",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-prod-manifests",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-content",
        "arn:aws:s3:::owlette-dev-manifests"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
